cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR

This paper deals with computer vision tasks such as object detection, 3D pose estimation, and sub-category recognition. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper proposes a hierarchical representation to jointly model these tasks, which involves machine learning techniques such as deep learning and optimization. Hence, it could also belong to cs.RO (Robotics), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.GR (Graphics).
